fetch() HTTP request bhejta hai

Chahe localhost ho, phir bhi network layer use hoti hai

Agar:

Internet / network disabled âŒ

Server (Tomcat / Spring Boot) band âŒ



â¡ï¸ Request fail ho jaayegi


---

ğŸ” Clear rule samjho

Case	Net chahiye?

fetch() / axios()	âœ… Haan
JSP â†’ JS data pass	âŒ Nahi
Servlet â†’ JSP	âŒ Nahi
DB â†’ Servlet	âŒ Nahi
Pure offline (Tomcat local)	âŒ Nahi



---

âœ… Tumhare offline project ke liye Sahi tareeqa

âŒ Galat (tumhara wala)

fetch("/api/ships") // net / server request

âœ… Sahi (Offline JSP way)

<script>
    const shipList = [];

    <c:forEach var="ship" items="${shipList}">
        shipList.push({
            id: "${ship.id}",
            name: "${ship.name}"
        });
    </c:forEach>

    console.log("Ship List:", shipList);
</script>


---

ğŸ§  Ek line mein samjho

> fetch = network call = net required
JSP data injection = no network = offline OK




